In this article, President Trump discusses the importance of promoting and purchasing products that are made in America. He believes that when goods are produced domestically, it strengthens the economy and creates jobs for American citizens. He criticizes previous government policies that have incentivized the movement of production overseas, resulting in the loss of industries and slow economic growth. Trump emphasizes the need to protect American industry and workers, stating that his administration is working towards providing a level playing field for American businesses. He highlights the creation of over a million new jobs this year and expresses optimism for the future, where America will be stronger and citizens will be prioritized.